CatDescriptText: Cutline of image published in Pittsburgh Courier newspaper, March 25, 1961, pg. B5 reads: "Enjoying Chi Affair - More Chi's and their guests, who enjoyed the swank affair at the Pittsburgh Hilton are shown in these three photographs. In the first photo, left to right, at eh table of Dr. and Mrs. Garfield Nickens, are: Louis Mason Jr., Mrs. Robert Williams, Atty. Everett Utterback, Mrs. Louis Mason, Dr. and Mrs. Nickens, William Houston, Mrs. Houston, Robert (Pappy) Williams and Mrs. Everett Utterback..."
TitMainTitle: Louis Mason Jr., Mrs. Robert Williams, Atty. Everett Utterback Sr., Mrs. Louis Mason, Dr. Garfield Nickens, Mrs. Nickens, William Houston, Mrs. Houston, Robert "Pappy" Williams, and Bernice Utterback, seated at banquet table in Hilton Hotel for Chi Delta Mu supper dance
